  <brief_title>Dual Diagnosis (Psychosis and Cannabismisuse): Comparison of Specialized Treatment Versus Unspecified Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Dual Diagnosis Psychosis and Substance Abuse: Short- and Middle-term Changes in Symptomatology After Visiting a Group Education Programme to Reduce Consumption of Cannabis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
